            "korean": "엘리베이터가 고장 났어요.",
            "romanization": "ellibeitteoga gojang nasseoyo.",
            "meaning": "The elevator doesn't work."
          }
        ],
        "culturalTip": "고장이 나면 관리사무소나 AS센터에 연락해요.",
        "explanationEn": "It is used when a machine or object is not functioning.",
        "whenToUseEn": "When Reporting a Malfunction",
        "culturalTipEn": "If something breaks down, contact the management office or the service center."
      }
    },
    {
