        "culturalTip": "긴급 상황에서는 112(경찰), 119(소방/응급)로 전화해요!",
        "explanationEn": "It means to officially report a problem or incident.",
        "whenToUseEn": "\"When notifying the police or relevant authorities\"",
        "culturalTipEn": "In an emergency, call 112 (police) or 119 (fire/ambulance)!"
